properties.name: Dalpura Canyon
properties.description: Dalpura is a relatively short canyon on the north side of the Grose Valley. It has one short abseil and the burnt out sections at the beginning of the canyon are a stark reminder of the late 2019/early 2020 bushfires. The walk in is not particularly tough, but a moderate level of fitness is required for the uphill walk out. A half day canyon!
